A. Auditing regulators
B. Lawful processing of personal data
C. Penetration testing
D. Network security only

14. ITAA 2008 Section 66 primarily deals with:
A. Civil compensation
B. Cyber offences and punishment
C. Privacy rights
D. Data classification

